clean_text:
15/10/24;
ok, I'm enough with this branch. super slow on drive thru. i claimed my promo burger use points, then this branch not available. congratulations, u just ruined my dinner. forever 1 star for u. not going to edit this post anymore.

10/10/23;
I just updated from 3 stars to 4 stars, definitely an improvement from most my previous purchased. They even answer my feedback and solved all my issue. Good work and keep it up I can say. See u in next update.

05/05/23;
recently their services n food did a great improvement. hope this will last n will be better finger cross. 🤞

1st old post;
happy meal without current season toys is no longer happy meal. I understand toys stock is limited n since is limited then u should just stop selling happy meal when there's no current season toys. don't sell something that u not able to fulfill it.

Based on my experience of having daily breakfast here (around 7am);
1. If you order nasi lemak, be careful of the cucumber, 9 out of 10 times they smell foul.

2. Anything with SCRAMBLED egg is sad and not even scrambled, refer to pic.
